Program: Discovery
Title: The aliens around us - archea
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrynt
Last Broadcast Date: 04 May 2004
Organisms that defy the conventional rules of biology. If we are to find life in the universe we may need to re-think our definition of a living organism, but we don't have to go into space to find creatures that live in unusual and unlikely places, known as archea